Interface FrameVertex2DSupplier

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Vertex2DSupplier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FixedFrameConvexPolygon2DBasics, FrameConvexPolygon2DBasics, FrameConvexPolygon2DReadOnly
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FrameConvexPolygon2D

    public interface FrameVertex2DSupplier
extends Vertex2DSupplier
    Implement this interface to create a custom supplier of 2D frame vertices or use the static methods to create default suppliers.
